{"tid":2448243,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣女團(DD52出嚟嘅)","createTime":"2021-03-15T19:15:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T23:17:34.000Z","uid":376741,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"236f11dfe78e9a911b35009a98fdeee84d958532","tid":2448243,"uid":376741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T19:15:22.000Z","msg":"最近真係狂loop DD52呢個選秀節目嘅歌，呢個節目目前出咗三隊女團(其中一隊唔係簽節目制作方嘅，係其他公司睇中佢哋而簽嘅)<br />\n先講喺節目出道嗰兩團：G.O.F.，行性感、台灣味路線；一團係Pun Fun，主打初戀系。<br />\n<br />\n先講<span class=\"red\">G.O.F</span><br />\nig: g.o.fofficial<br />\nG.O.F.係冠軍團嚟嘅，前身為《DD52》嘅「烈焰之心」，啲歌偏向台灣味同性感，最出名嘅係Fairy Temple<br />\n<br />\n比賽13人版：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/52kHu8fNcSE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F52kHu8fNcSE&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirC1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=fae81211\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/52kHu8fNcSE</a><br />\n<br />\n出道後MV 7人版：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QaLFW4bHQSY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQaLFW4bHQSY&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirC1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=ed0694e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QaLFW4bHQSY</a><br />\n<br />\n其實我個人覺得比賽版好睇同好聽好多，個氣勢足好多，但其實冇對比嘅話唔算差得好遠。<br />\n<br />\n另外有首應該同大家有親切感啲嘅，係有粵語嘅《悲傷基隆港》：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/F_tFmmzj3Os\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FF_tFmmzj3Os&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirC1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=8f8145ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/F_tFmmzj3Os</a><br />\n嗰陣聽到廣東話覺得好驚喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係G.O.F.嘅成員：<br />\n之絃(Dolly)：性感擔當<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcMT3ZZ6ZHPJehRkVJkUpcpntpSYC2koXo36RHYUJ2E8S?filename=D6DydRJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD6DydRJ.jpg&h=20c80de6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nig: xdolly04<br />\n<br />\n葛宸羽(阿寶)：主唱擔當<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmd5GYbKigkaiy2JS97CZu16nXH6S3srUSMP8iDUeeMKVS?filename=fiwPwDL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfiwPwDL.jpg&h=69720ee6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nig: ke_b.a.o_ <br />\n<br />\n曾薀帆(呆呆)：饒舌辣妹+吃貨擔當<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmU3nM4VyvQfeg8fnJ7vCLJH2XXbt18wAiASTMaizo8he7?filename=jmsryTU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjmsryTU.jpg&h=8f35a0f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n私心想放埋呢張：<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSz4fHsGsT1ZSAwCUhtvVjzvCtSroQT2Thm2V3pzLB2Vv?filename=ne36yUd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fne36yUd.jpg&h=c47466bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nig: demi59487 <br />\n<br />\n夏娜：綜藝/長腿擔當<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbGgTTRgUGTxi68bsdn5tFcEPDGLATNbbD5nM8xqn6b4A?filename=Mrz9wGL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMrz9wGL.jpg&h=345bc13c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nig: zzha_na19<br />\n<br />\n艾比(Abby)：甜美擔當<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRPkSuvY8TjWc6m8pQsesdmdfU3bnJ1tRjrvvQ2pzG9NG?filename=3QPtNfT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3QPtNfT.jpg&h=5af3723f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nig: abby28920 <br />\n<br />\n黑黑(Lisa)：隊長<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmf3XWH7GBpJWyTys3KLUx1VyvzF93ZBr19GDzPkUqHihU?filename=KQ172Qf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKQ172Qf.jpg&h=1e551cc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nig: lisa901224_<br />\n<br />\n蝶香(Rebecca)：主唱、忙內<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmT22uUMHdrnyddGbfvZqpKGdfbN5GibaQkpvCkYrb3QPw?filename=rNXyYpm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNXyYpm.jpg&h=5880c592&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n把聲真係好正，而且身材勁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(btw 蝶香係真名，佢本名就叫黃蝶香<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\nig: rebaecca.h<br />\n<br />\n佢哋個style好特別，唔係抄韓國日本，係真真正正嘅台灣style，幾乎每首歌都會有啲台語喺裡面(不得不說DD52啲音樂制作人好勁，50首原創真心好正)<br />\n<br />\n等陣講埋人氣團Pink Fun同俾其他公司簽嘅HUR"},{"pid":"3d7472632f108c12a8b150075993cff084d907e1","tid":2448243,"uid":376741,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T19:44:27.000Z","msg":"人氣團Pink Fun：<br />\n前身為《DD52》嘅粉紅梅花，主打初戀系<br />\n最新MV：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6ova2DItjG0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6ova2DItjG0&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirC1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=5402f316\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6ova2DItjG0</a><br />\n<br />\n比賽最出名嗰兩首：<br />\n決賽嘅《粉紅炸彈》<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/g7LOyi_KDPQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fg7LOyi_KDPQ&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirC1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=6ff6e602\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/g7LOyi_KDPQ</a><br />\n<br />\n比賽主打歌：《告訴你一個秘密》<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4j8DtRrWqSM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4j8DtRrWqSM&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirC1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=366756b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4j8DtRrWqSM</a><br />\n<br />\n成員：<br />\n珮含 @pei._.0709<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmeq1hXmYyHQoNGynVZUGESUgsGU1V7e8mjBzs9aEWwbMr?filename=TkFQgny.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTkFQgny.jpg&h=f0c84ad3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n心平 @_sin_ping<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmX91PHYkyLXwGJp6XLEBDennqAvNHxvXAQiKQ97f2HVho?filename=LZXWbV2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLZXWbV2.jpg&h=7567dfb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巧瑜 @chiaoyu_95<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSag1jtqMzcXxiEkLWdzyuotZZ7ywZhuP4uZNBR5CPxwx?filename=JqvXFPG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJqvXFPG.jpg&h=6af6d9a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br /